Steve LIPSCOMB, Appellant, v. F. G. ZERBST, Warden, United States Penitentiary, Atlanta, Ga., Appellee. No. 8608. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. Oct. 12, 1937. . Lawrence S. Camp, U. S. Atty., and Harvey H. Tysinger and H. T. Nichols, Asst. U. S. Attys., all of Atlanta, Ga., for appellee.

Before FOSTER, SIBLEY, and HOLMES, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment is affirmed.
